description.en: Woonkly is a DeFi protocol that empowers a Decentralized Social Network in which the capital invested in post advertising by the advertisers is shared with the people who interact with that content (Post, Photo, Video, Podcast); all created and working 100% in Blockchain using our own mainnet (Hyperledger BESU and Polkadot) connected with Binance Smart Chain (BSC).
